1. Ispostavilo se da je moja procena bila tačna. (*Ispostavilo*) (It turned out that my estimate was correct.)
2. Kada se sve *ispostavi*, znaćemo šta je uzrok problema. (se *ispostavi*) (When everything is revealed, we will know what the cause of the problem is.)
3. Većina ljudi ne zna šta će se *ispostaviti* u budućnosti. (se *ispostaviti*) (Most people don't know what will turn out in the future.)
4. Kada sam pozvao policiju, *ispostavilo* se da je to bio pravi potez. (*Ispostavilo*) (When I called the police, it turned out to be the right move.)
5. Oni su imali plan, ali se *ispostavilo* da nije bilo tako jednostavno. (*Ispostavilo*) (They had a plan, but it turned out it wasn't that simple.)